Package civitas.celestis.object

Class BaseObject

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.object.BaseObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Movable, Physical, Renderable, Tickable, Unique
Direct Known Subclasses:
ImmovableObject
public class BaseObject extends Object implements Unique, Movable, Renderable, Physical, Tickable
A basic object which can be placed in a world.
